  Locus:
    Page: 327
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Moderation
---
There is a proper measure in all things, certain limits beyond which and
short of which right is not to be found. ... Who so cultivates the golden
mean avoids the poverty of a hovel and the envy of a palace.
